      "description": "This E46 M3 is a driver-focused example featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, renowned for its individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing. The drivetrain is anchored by a Getrag six-speed manual transmission and a mechanical limited-slip differential, providing an analog tactile experience. Recent service history includes a comprehensive cooling system overhaul and subframe inspection to ensure structural rigidity. The suspension utilizes a refined MacPherson strut and multi-link setup, maintaining excellent turn-in response and lateral stability. While displaying minor aesthetic wear indicative of spirited use, the mechanical vitals are robust, offering a visceral 8,000 RPM redline performance for the discerning purist.",
